&lt;Redorin&gt;
</FONT></TD>
<TD><FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana, Arial">Hiding is a ability of certain races. You can find it in the abilities(I think thats what the button says) list in the lower right hand corner. Dark elves have it while Humans don't. It all depends on your race.<P>Any buffs you cast on yourself(excluding dots) you can click off using your mouse pointer and the left mouse button. You can also click off SoW from other players.</FONT>
</TD></TR>

<TR bgcolor="#DEDFDF">
<TD valign=top>
<FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana, Arial">
skinni stonefinger
</FONT></TD>
<TD><FONT SIZE="2" FACE="Verdana, Arial">cast invisibility on yourself to release pet, he will come for you anyways though. But it breaks charm and your party can kill it. Root is helpful beforehand and so is having memblur handy.</FONT>
</TD></TR>

